# Static Site Conventions

- Use semantic HTML (`header`, `main`, `section`, `nav`, `footer`)
- Keep styles in `style.css`; use `assets/css/variables.css` for shared tokens
- Reference CSS variables from `:root` (e.g. `var(--text-100)`, `var(--accent)`, `var(--bg-card)`)
- SVG assets: prefer inline or `<img>` from `assets/svg/`
- Typography: Syne (headings), DM Sans (body)
